{"lastModified":1761160206676,"uri":"c::18263540498::vessel::28f03ba0-8a98-11f0-8b99-db21657ac9d0","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe Bali 4.1 represents a groundbreaking evolution in catamaran design, emphasizing comfort and ergonomic living spaces. It offers spacious and fully optimized areas for living, perfect for enjoying every moment on board.\n\nThe interior layout includes four generous cabins, each with its own private bathroom, ensuring privacy and comfort for all guests. Additionally, it provides two skipper berths, allowing the presence of two professionals for maximum safety and support during the journey.\n\nA distinctive feature of the Bali 4.1 is the aft platform, which offers extra space for relaxation and entertainment close to the water. The catamaran is equipped with a full bimini top, providing shade and sun protection over the deck while creating a welcoming area for unwinding.\n\nOne of its standout features is the water-maker system, enabling self-sufficiency on board so you can enjoy extended trips without frequent stops for resupply. Furthermore, the Bali 4.1 is equipped with modern amenities, making it ideal for leisure travel by blending practicality with luxury.\n\nOverall, the Bali 4.1 is the perfect choice for those seeking a comfortable and reliable way to explore the Aegean and other seas, offering safety, autonomy, and a unique on-water experience.","blueprint":{"name":"NORTHCAT II","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::28f03ba0-8a98-11f0-8b99-db21657ac9d0::assets::08919d10-8a9b-11f0-8bc8-a70d4f4cabc3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::28f03ba0-8a98-11f0-8b99-db21657ac9d0::assets::08901670-8a9b-11f0-8bc8-a70d4f4cabc3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::28f03ba0-8a98-11f0-8b99-db21657ac9d0::assets::089d83f0-8a9b-11f0-bd44-5d9b7193b46c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::28f03ba0-8a98-11f0-8b99-db21657ac9d0::assets::088f5320-8a9b-11f0-8bc8-a70d4